         <div type="apparatus">
            <p>b: The letters reported from Boulanger's copy in ALA are found on the new fragment.</p>
            <p>c: The join in c, at the <foreign xml:lang="grc">Μ</foreign> of <foreign xml:lang="grc">κεράμου</foreign> appears certain. although the blocks cannot now be moved to bring them together.</p>
