         <div type="translation">
            <p>Dionysios, son of Photeinos, doctor <supplied cert="low" reason="lost">built this for the purpose of pleasure</supplied> and rest <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
               <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">building</supplied> up to the tiled roof, with the <gap reason="lost" unit="character" extent="unknown"/>
            </p>
